<div class="bg-darker-700 w-full sm:py-48 py-24 sm:px-10 px-4">
  <div class="max-w-6xl flex lg:flex-row flex-col m-auto">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:mb-0 mr-10">
      <div class="text-purple-300 font-black mr-20 font-serif sm:text-7xl text-4xl sm:my-10 my-4">
        Learning, <em>the easy way</em>
      </div>
      <div class="text-lg sm:text-2xl text-lincoln-50 font-light">
        typecraft is a place where we can all learn together, and have fun doing it.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="m-auto rounded-lg">
      <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/H70lULWJeig" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="m-auto flex flex-col w-full py-32 bg-darker-900 sm:px-10 px-4">
  <div class="max-w-6xl m-auto">
    <div class="sm:text-6xl text-4xl font-serif font-black text-cyan-700">Hot off the press</div>
    <div class="sm:text-2xl font-light text-lg w-full mt-4 text-lincoln-50">
      The latest from typecraft. This community is all about learning, together. All of these posts accompany a video lesson, so you can learn by watching, and then practice by typing.
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-row justify-evenly mt-20">
      <% @posts.each do |post| %>
        <%= link_to post do %>
          <div class="max-w-sm bg-darker-800 hover:shadow-darker-600 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
            <% if post.thumbnail.present? %>
              <%= image_tag post.thumbnail, class: "w-full" %>
            <% end %>
            <div class="px-6 py-4">
              <div class="font-serif font-bold text-cyan-400 text-xl mb-2">
                <%= post.title %>
              </div>
              <p class="text-dark-100 text-base">
              <%= post.blurb %>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
